{"tid":756461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大連跨海大橋橋墩現裂縫　設計者：正常伸縮縫","createTime":"2018-07-26T05:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T10:10:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fa206daa60db453450b958f3d61d1cdbf2e42f","tid":756461,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180725/s00004/19d5f728d82ea3afe7c9e84118e44754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F19d5f728d82ea3afe7c9e84118e44754.jpg&h=9278c45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國基建工程屢有隱憂，有網民近日於遼寧大連星海灣一座跨海大橋橋墩上，發現一道極明顯裂縫，讓人憂慮工程質量。事件發酵後，設計者及大橋管理方先後接受傳媒訪問，指裂縫是正常的伸縮縫設計，用作抵禦大橋因冷縮熱脹而變形。<br />\n<br />\n設計者應旭永稱，有關裂縫術語為伸縮縫。用以防止橋樑結構因溫度變形而被破壞的設計，是任何橋樑都需要的結構。他又稱，因星海灣大橋有雙層設計，墩樑連接有別於一般橋樑，加上施工質素參差，導致伸縮縫不平整，從而給人橋體混凝土破裂的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n至於身為大橋管理方的星海灣開發建設管理中心，他們稱昨日（24日）早上已派員修補裂縫理，同時全面檢查大橋所有橋墩及相應的設施查，保證橋體美觀效果，又承諾今後將增派人員巡查大橋，並定期邀請專家檢測。<br />\n<br />\n星海灣跨海大橋2015年10月開通，全長6公里，是東北地區最長的跨海大橋工程，也是中國首座海上地錨懸索式跨海大橋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180725/s00004/1532488049734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F1532488049734&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a679120e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F1532488049734&h=ef86d858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180725/s00004/1532488049734</a>"},{"pid":"193d80742d4d1e5037c22f3e04557d955167fad6","tid":756461,"uid":40950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"又話伸縮縫，又補留佢？<br />\n張來點伸縮呀師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚先答啦專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc73c3934bda85c51d65dcdd5de049e75ad3ea0d","tid":756461,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n申縮事件"},{"pid":"c76358992a409e2a8a89639a0d470f79e70bb502","tid":756461,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc73c3934bda85c51d65dcdd5de049e75ad3ea0d","tid":756461,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n申縮事件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}